tps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fyre-festival-billy-mcfarland@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fyre-festival-billy-mcfarland@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fyre-festival-billy-mcfarland@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fyre-festival-2-confirmed-for-2025-has-yet-to-book-any-artists-3792163">Fyre Festival</a>宣布了今年“真实回报”的日期，位置和门票 - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/festivals-blog/fyre-festival-luxury-chaos-pictures-2061836#TWfKse5rOmohkHUp.99">Fyre Festival：这是有史以来最糟糕的“豪华”节吗？</a></strong></li></ul><p> 2017年，费尔音乐节（Fyre Festival）席卷了世界 - 不是因为它的阵容和成功，而是因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/festivals-blog/fyre-festival-luxury-chaos-pictures-2061836#TWfKse5rOmohkHUp.99">臭名昭著的计划和粉丝体验</a>导致了几项诉讼和纪录片。</p><p>经过多年的创始人比利·麦克法兰（Billy McFarland）的戏弄，该节日将于今年返回，现在已经确认了卷土重来，费尔音乐节和麦克法兰（Fyre Festival）和麦克法兰（McFarland）邀请社交媒体宣布关键细节。 </p><figure id="attachment_3792350" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792350" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792350" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/andy-king-billy-mcfarland-fyre-2014.jpg" alt="安迪·金和比利·麦克法兰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/andy-king-billy-mcfarland-fyre-2014.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/andy-king-billy-mcfarland-fyre-2014-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/andy-king-billy-mcfarland-fyre-2014-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/andy-king-billy-mcfarland-fyre-2014-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/andy-king-billy-mcfarland-fyre-2014-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/andy-king-billy-mcfarland-fyre-2014-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3792350" class="wp-caption-text">安迪·金（Andy King）和比利·麦克法兰（Billy McFarland）于2014年8月7日在格林威治大街22号举行的登山晚宴派对（信用：帕特里克·麦克穆兰（Patrick McMullan）/帕特里克·麦克穆兰（Patrick McMullan）</figcaption></figure><p> McFarland和Fyre Festival围绕标语“ Fyre Festival 2是真实的”，已确认其第二次尝试将于5月30日至6月2日在墨西哥的Isla Mujeres举行。<a href="https://www.fyre.mx/explore" target="_blank" rel="noopener">门票现在售价</a>在1,400美元之间，八票套餐的票价高达110万美元。</p><p>该节日被描述为“三天逃往墨西哥加勒比海的三天，您将每天与您最喜欢的人才一起探索，并在晚上聚在一起与音乐一起庆祝”。</p><p> Fyre Festival 2还声称，它将以“由国际和当地人才领导的冒险活动，每天将客人乘坐边界进行游览，并在夜间团结私密的海滩表演”。 </p><p></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGdUf2lxOab/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.