罗伯特·帕丁森（Robert Pattinson）的蝙蝠侠不会在詹姆斯·冈恩（James Gunn）的DC宇宙中https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-pattinsons-batman-will-not-not-be-be-in-james-gunns-gunns-dc-universe-3840958?ut m_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = robert-pattinsons-batman-batman-will-will-not-be-in-james-gunns-gunns-dc-universeSurej Singh Tue, 25 Feb 2025 02:43:51 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3840958 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>取而代之的是，冈恩（Gunn</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-pattinsons-batman-will-not-be-in-james-gunns-dc-universe-3840958">罗伯特·帕丁森（Robert Pattinson）的蝙蝠侠将不会出现在詹姆斯·冈恩（James Gunn）的DC宇宙中，</a>这是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>首先出现的。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/robert-pattinson-batman@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>已经确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-pattinson">罗伯特·帕丁森</a>（Robert Pattinson）的蝙蝠侠将不会成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-gunn">詹姆斯·冈恩（James Gunn</a> ）的DC宇宙的一部分。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mickey-17-preview-screening-event-tickets-nme-screens-robert-pattinson-3837085">NME屏幕宣布“米奇17”预览筛选事件</a></strong></li></ul><p>自从Gunn <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/henry-cavill-not-returning-superman-dc-james-gunn-3367115">控制DC Studios担任联合首席执行官</a>和即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/superman"><em>超人</em></a>电影的导演以来，粉丝一直在大声疾呼Pattinson的Batman版本，并将其纳入Gunn的DC Universe。</p><p>但是，冈恩现在消除了发生这种情况的所有可能性。在最近的新闻<a href="https://screenrant.com/james-gunn-robert-pattinson-not-dcu-batman-story-update-brave-and-the-bold/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>发布会</em></a>上，冈恩说，当被问及帕丁森是否将包括在他的DC Slate中时：“当然不是计划。” </p><figure id="attachment_3189842" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3189842" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3189842" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/thebatman-robertpattinson-2000x1270-2.jpg" alt="罗伯特·帕丁森（Robert Pattinson）在“蝙蝠侠”中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/thebatman-robertpattinson-2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/thebatman-robertpattinson-2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/thebatman-robertpattinson-2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/thebatman-robertpattinson-2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/thebatman-robertpattinson-2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/thebatman-robertpattinson-2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3189842" class="wp-caption-text">罗伯特·帕丁森（Robert Pattinson）在《蝙蝠侠》（The Batman）（2022）中。学分：DC Entertainment/Warner Bros。 /专辑</figcaption></figure><p>冈恩（Gunn）的联合首席执行官彼得·萨弗兰（Peter Safran）提供了更多的解释，分享了他们“爱”帕丁森（Pattinson）的看法，但他们专注于在即将上映的电影<em>《勇敢和大胆</em>》中介绍自己的蝙蝠侠版本： &#39;ve必须将蝙蝠侠引入DCU。当务之急。那就是<em>勇敢和大胆</em>的计划。”</p><p> Safran还补充说，DC Studios是“在<em>勇敢和大胆的</em>非常积极的发展中，这个故事也很好地融合在一起”，“我们很快就会为您提供更多的事情。”</p><p>到目前为止，帕丁森仅在马特·里夫（Matt Reeve）备受赞誉的2022年电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-batman"><em>《蝙蝠侠》（The Batman）</em></a>中仅描绘了斗篷十字军。 </p><figure id="attachment_3171677" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3171677" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3171677" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson.jpg" alt="蝙蝠侠" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/The_Batman_Robert_Pattinson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3171677" class="wp-caption-text">罗伯特·帕丁森（Robert Pattinson）首次亮相蝙蝠侠。信用：华纳兄弟。</figcaption></figure><p>去年12月，华纳兄弟（Warner Bros.）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-batman-2-has-been-delayed-to-2027-3825040">宣布，备受期待的<em>《蝙蝠侠2》（Batman 2）</em>被推迟了一年</a>，新发布的日期为2027年10月1<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-batman-2-starts-filming-later-this-year-3838019">日</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/the-batman-2-release-date-cast-plot-trailer-3341153">这是我们对“蝙蝠侠2”的了解</a></strong></li></ul><p><i>NME</i>在<i>《蝙蝠侠》</i>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-batman-review-robert-pattinson-3171137">四星级审查</a>中写道：“导演马特·里夫斯（Matt Reeves）将坚韧的暴民戏剧与电影 - 非电影侦探惊悚片混合在一起，这要归功于达诺（Dano）的超级恐怖反派，这也是一些心理<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/horror">恐怖</a>。大多数时候，它出色地脱颖而出。”</p><p> <i>NME</i>还称赞Kravitz对Catwoman的描绘，称她为角色“完美”：“这里，里夫斯给克拉维兹提供了适当的背景故事，并通过肮脏的夜总会和废弃的建筑工地告诉了它。”</p><p>里夫斯（Reeves）的标志性故事的版本导致<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-penguin-review-the-batman-spin-off-colin-farrell-3792209">衍生出探索科林·法雷尔（Colin Farrell）的企鹅角色</a>。<i>企鹅</i>去年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/hbo-max">Max</a>上发行，由于罢工而遭受了生产的延迟。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-pattinsons-batman-will-not-be-in-james-gunns-dc-universe-3840958">罗伯特·帕丁森（Robert Pattinson）的蝙蝠侠将不会出现在詹姆斯·冈恩（James Gunn）的DC宇宙中，</a>这是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>首先出现的。</p> ;
